# File Structure Rules

## Project Root (trac-portal-ui/)
- v2/               → New Vue 3 + Vite application
- app/              → Legacy Nuxt application (to be removed)
- ROADMAP.md        → Project plan and decisions log

## Source Structure (v2/src/)
```
v2/
├── src/
│   ├── assets/
│   │   └── styles/
│   │       └── globals.css      → Tailwind + CSS variables
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── ui/                  → shadcn-vue (auto-generated, don't edit)
│   │   ├── layout/              → AppSidebar, BottomNav, PageHeader
│   │   ├── forms/               → NetForm, UserForm, OperatorForm
│   │   └── features/            → NetCard, AttendeeList, StatCard
│   ├── composables/             → useAuth, useApi, useToast
│   ├── lib/                     → Utility functions (cn, etc.)
│   ├── pages/                   → Route views
│   │   ├── auth/                → LoginPage, RegisterPage
│   │   ├── dashboard/           → DashboardPage
│   │   ├── nets/                → NetListPage, NetDetailPage
│   │   ├── operators/           → OperatorListPage
│   │   └── settings/            → SettingsPage
│   ├── router/                  → Vue Router configuration
│   ├── stores/                  → Pinia stores
│   ├── types/                   → TypeScript interfaces
│   ├── App.vue
│   └── main.ts
├── index.html
├── package.json
├── vite.config.ts
├── tailwind.config.ts
└── tsconfig.json
```

## Naming Conventions
- Components: PascalCase (NetCard.vue)
- Composables: useCamelCase (useAuth.ts)
- Stores: camelCase (auth.ts) exporting useAuthStore
- Pages: PascalCase + Page suffix (LoginPage.vue)
- Types: PascalCase + interface/type (NetResponse, UserType)

## Import Aliases
- @/ → src/
- @/components → src/components
- @/composables → src/composables